high_descs: Turn left, go to the left side of the sink
Pick up the soap on the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the bath
Put the soap in the bath
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the basket
Pick up the soap in the basket
Turn right, go forward, turn right at the bath
Put the soap in the bath
anns.task_desc: Put two soaps in the bath

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink's counter then take a tiny step left.
Pick up the pink bar of soap that's in front of you near the wall.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right.
Put the bar of soap in the tub by the green wash cloth.
Turn right and walk to the shower then turn right to face the small garbage on the  floor.
Pick up the bar of soap that's in the garbage.
Walk back to where you put the first bar of soap.
Put this bar of soap above the first one in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn left, go to sink closest to garbage can.
Pick up pink soap from counter to the left of the sink and right of garbage can.
Turn right, go to wall.  Turn right, go to tub.
Put soap in tub to left, in front of dirty cloth.
Turn right, go to shower stall, turn right, go to wall.
Get soap out of garbage can left of counter and right of shower stall.
Turn right, go to tub.  Turn right.
Put soap in tub, to right of other soap and dirty cloth.
anns.task_desc: Move soap from counter and garbage can into tub.
